data.description: MOVE RIGHT IN to this luxurious home at Champions Gate and Treat yourself to the VIP neighborhood.  This BEAUTIFUL Two-Story home, 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home is located in the #1 requested residential community. This open floorplan combines the kitchen, dining room, and family room into a spacious GREAT ROOM.  LARGE KITCHEN features stone countertops, stainless steel appliances, a breakfast bar, and a closet pantry. The first floor has upgraded tile throughout the public areas. The area is known for its luxury homes and resort-style amenities. Some of the benefits of buying a home in Champions Gate include access to world-class golf courses, a water park, and a variety of restaurants and shops. It’s only minutes away from WALT DISNEY WORLD and other theme parks. Golfers will love the proximity to Champions Gate Golf Resort, the headquarters of the Leadbetter Golf Academy. The area is also conveniently located near major highways, making it easy to get to other parts of Florida. Buying a home in Champions Gate offers unbeatable perks, such as the option to use your property as an investment as you see fit. PET-FRIENDLY community. GATED Community. The new owner(s) will have access to four clubhouses RESORTS at Champions Gate: 1. Oasis Clubhouse, which has a restaurant, theater, game room, lazy river, resort-style pool, tennis court, kiddie splash zone, and much more. 2. The Retreat at Champions Gate Clubhouse with a Movie Room, Games Room, Grille Room Restaurant, Fitness Center, Aerobics Room, and Family Friendly 3. Champions Gate Club and 4. Champions Gate Condos.  Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom dream home that seamlessly combines elegance, functionality, and comfort. Schedule a viewing today and let this enchanting haven become your perfect retreat. Welcome home!
